<Paragraph>This sample illustrates the conversion of a MS Excel document to a PDF document.</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>Essential XlsIO supports to convert an Excel workbook into a PDF document. Also supports to convert Excel chart, AutoShapes into PDF.</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Supports conversion of an Excel document to PDF document</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Installation of Essential PDF and ExcelChartToImageConverter is necessary to run this sample</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>  
